source: https://sourceforge.net/projects/cppcheck/files/cppcheck/
version: 1.82
date: 2018-01-14
build cmd:
sudo apt-get install libpcre3-dev
make SRCDIR=build CFGDIR=cfg HAVE_RULES=yes CXXFLAGS="-O2 -DNDEBUG -Wall -Wno-sign-compare -Wno-unused-function"

changed:
fixed odd whitespaces in rules with the following commands:
```
dos2unix <list of files>
sed -i 's/[ \t]*$//' tools/cppcheck/cfg/bsd.cfg
sed -i 's/[ \t]*$//' tools/cppcheck/cfg/cppcheck-cfg.rng
sed -i 's/[ \t]*$//' tools/cppcheck/cfg/gnu.cfg
sed -i 's/[ \t]*$//' tools/cppcheck/cfg/posix.cfg
sed -i 's/[ \t]*$//' tools/cppcheck/cfg/windows.cfg
```

usage:
tools/cppcheck/cppcheck --error-exitcode=1 --std=c++11 --std=posix --platform=unix64 --enable=all --inconclusive -Isrc ./src ./test
